Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you the info on this\NElbaji guy and his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cammy, I'm not seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to that Tilarna girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's in the sleeping room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a new city. It's tiring her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's with the sword, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I took my eyes off her\Nfor a minute and she split.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring her back. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want people complaining\Nabout the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, a hyperspace gate\Nappeared in the middle of the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the gate lay a strange world\Nfilled with fairies and monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariaena Island. The city of San-Teresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is Earth's "front door."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over two million citizens\Nfrom both worlds live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A mixture of different races and\Ndiverse cultures, haves and have-nots...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's newest "city of dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the shadows of all this\Nchaos lurked countless crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs. Prostitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The San-Teresa Metropolitan Police maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a special unit to deal with these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Without my help, you'd have been turned\Naway at the front door, Sister Tilarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful to the God of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your "God" help with fake IDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've preferred\Na more normal outfit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it look like it's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On Earth, high-ranking women walk like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah! Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's wonderful, Brother Kenny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Play some damn disco music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't that kind of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure about this, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother gave it to me.\NBut I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Brother.\NLet's have some fun while we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But Father, she seemed like\Nsomething was really bothering her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids that age have a lot on their mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her get some experience\Nwith different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like O, or V, or A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get lost.\N--Aww, lighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a noble from the Tiburani area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from your world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then why didn't you speak to me in Farbani?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought the language of the doreany\Nwould be more suited for a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Speak as you like. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Great, all that fancy\Nnoble language tires me the hell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we talk like this instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hitting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I love girls like you.\NHow about we go have a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone. Bother somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dennis Elbaji. The guy who runs this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dennis... Dennis. Oh, Dennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dennis Elbaji's a friend of mine.\NWant an introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make that face. Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm Dennis Elbaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tilarna Exedilica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sent here by the Knights of Mirvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A knight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back the fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That's product.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you're ready to die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done talking, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Incompetents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens when\Nyou rely on doreany weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days are just wimps.\NIt's a real problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see your panties, Tilarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kill you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of questions, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This area hasn't been developed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There're still traces of the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody lives here anymore.\NThey all moved to the doreany town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't make a single dollar\Nraising crops, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the name of Earth's god?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Money."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Simplest thing in the world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've converted to its religion, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zelada, the goods are ready, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If you'll follow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Knights of Mirvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She found my club somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask her all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make her tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mr. Kareem, let's finish the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An old temple in the Hightails.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Matched the records the delivery people had.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SWAT's on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When will they get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That long? Make them hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to move up the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the questioning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, now I'm Don Quixote.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Arms of great strength.\NProtection of the war god.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you need to stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll say it.\NThis is the police. Throw down your--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the fairy? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worse for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes cash to make\Nthe drugs I turn them into.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there was the investment\Nto make my new product.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the place is going up in flames.\NIt's depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The fairies are holy and inviolable beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my new product.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use a fairy as a medium
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn everyone within a few kilometers\Ninto fairy dust addicts instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychic bomb, you could call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to come up\Nwith a cooler name, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer even human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Human... Human, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up in the same world you did.\NMy family were warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword fighting. Mounted combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Etiquette. Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to master it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I was gonna spend the rest of my life\Nbeing bossed around by incompetent nobles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,before dying in some\Nstupid fight over territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ends a life lived with honor.\NDisgusting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Earth's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the American dream, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said? Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With money, you can have whatever you want.\NThis place is much more human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're another one of the morons, huh?\NThat's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be no holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance, dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! A little more and\Nyour boobs will come spilling out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I only had my sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance. That sword. Vreideni style, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. I'm not giving you a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My deepest thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher's name is Lord Garada Vreideni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell it to the demons in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done. I would turned tail and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a scary dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a fierce enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't stare at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the kind of clothing I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. She's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense any latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The real one is getting further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet. I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Those footprints are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That red wizard took the bomb\Nshe was trapped in and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychic bomb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I understand the particulars,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but that explains what happens\Nto the guys from Precinct 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That wizard, Zelada, took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If he uses it, the results will be horrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tens of thousands of people\Nturned into addicts in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And he can make them do\Nwhatever he wants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet. She's very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands up. Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the undercover\Ncop from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna pay for what you did to Rick.\NYou're spending the rest of your life in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do that to an old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Show a little mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Matoba, looks like you caught the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,SWAT's cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They caught the terrorists\Nwho were buying the bomb, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hear. But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Use my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest thanks, Sir Roth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw down the gun, Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right... Sir Matoba, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely recognized you from\Nthe time we met in that swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You wiped out my unit during the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a lovely evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Matoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the one informing him\Nabout the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who gave you an inexperienced\NSemanian to slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who had an assassin sent after Alvarez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And told Zelada that the temple\Nhideout had been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And killed Rick, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fury had almost found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Roth, you of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He and I want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That man, Zelada, hates Earth's civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants terrorism to sow hatred\Nbetween Earth and the Semanians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Coexistence and peace\Nare lies the idealists tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can never understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:18:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are adapting just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And their ability to adapt is what scares me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at their vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Three generations from now,\Nthey'll be ruling the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The invasion will be over\Nbefore anybody realizes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Even the invaders\Ndon't know they're doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The world needs to know\Nhow dangerous they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that psychic bomb can make them afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without damaging the infrastructure of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,An officer? But more importantly,\NI'm a human living on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei Matoba, I thought you might understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to join you? Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You always hide a revolver at your ankle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like a dad to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither can I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Zelada?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna use that bomb. And right now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the chief's car.\NForest Tower, in Queen's Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei. About the chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk later.\NGet some officers there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Forest Tower is one of the\Ntallest buildings in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to use the psychic bomb there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be more effective\Nthere than on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a nuke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this place like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Loaded with rich folks.\NCommon folk never go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not even worth stopping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That wizard... Zelada... You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? To me, he's just another perp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that wizard Zelada's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A wizard's power is something to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They can blind a warrior\Nor create poisonous flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weapons are no match...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even this thing? It's a good gun,\Nand I've been using it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your doreany weapons have no soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I feel a faint latena from this gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Feelings put into an object,\Nno matter what it is, will create latena.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay close to me, Kei. I'm the only one\Nwho can spot the enemy's ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're my partner, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahead! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That fire will burn your lungs.\NYou won't be able to breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll choke to death, huh? Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Leahyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next time"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}COP CRAFT.{\i0}
